overview: All 13 episodes of the original program Hello Pro no Oshigoto Challenge, which was broadcasted on dTV Channel's Hikari TV Channel+ streaming service in spring 2019, have been re-edited to include unreleased scenes for this DVD. Joujou Gundan's Suzuki Keita provides the narration! Disc 1 (60mins), Disc 2 (62mins).
title: Hello! Project DVD Magazine Vol.64
